# Fresh Guess environment variables (all OPTIONAL).
#
# By default the app scrapes Rotten Tomatoes with Playwright at runtime to read
# the public Algolia search credentials it embeds in its page, so no env vars
# are required for local development.
#
# Set these to SKIP Playwright entirely (recommended for production / serverless
# where a Chromium binary isn't available). They are server-only — do NOT use a
# VITE_ prefix, or the key would be exposed to the browser.
#
# RT_ALGOLIA_APP_ID=79FRDP12PN
# RT_ALGOLIA_SEARCH_KEY=175588f6e5f8319b27702e4cc4013561
# RT_ALGOLIA_INDEX=content_rt
